				<td colspan="2"><span>/wave Zingin
<br />

<br />
if you have the group to support you ...mpg is doable at 65.  I did it to exhaustion at 66 when omens was released.  6-way can be pulled single without hitting fade once.  You just need to be judicious and patient about your pulls.  Splitting the PHs for the 2 close named however is likely to cost you at least one fade.  So its hardly the ideal camp if you don't have the mana pool and fades in you.  Once the 6-way center area is broken ...its a nice spot to run your mobs around and debuff and slow them.
<br />

<br />
If you are required to be the CC for the group either by mezz or simply by ensuring pulls are single...then insist on the blind hunter camp.
<br />

<br />
WoS is more far mana intensive I have found...</span></td>
