				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: A little help on MPG<a name="72970"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Feb 7 05 6:25 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Im guessing by 6 way you mean the spot just north of Odiumate Isienne's spawn point. On Terris Thule we call that the courtyard (or CY). If thats the case you can pull the whole area without lull and Ill go over the steps that I use to pull the whole area including Kuruon, Ghio, and Odi or their placeholders.
<br />

<br />
For this to work your group has to be at the south wall where the courtyard opens up and to pull Ghio without adds effectivly you must have Fading memories and the level 67 or 70 mezz song. 
<br />

<br />
1. Pull the discordling in front of your camp. 
<br />
2. run into the open area and turn west to see a lightning warrior. Wait for the west wanderer (usually a kyv, ukun, or noc) to move north then pull the lightning warrior to your group. 
<br />
3. Run out to the same spot in step 2 and pull the west wanderer that I mentioned. 
<br />
4. Run out to the same spot in step 2 and pull the east wanderer (usually a kyv or Ikaav). 
<br />
5. Run out and follow the southwest hall down and pull a Huvval to your group. 
<br />
6. Go back down the same hall as in 5 and continue further to find a large pillar with a dragorn by it. Pull the Dragorn.
<br />
7. Go down the hall again following the large open area south till you see a hall going west. Go into that hall and look north for a large circular area. Pull the discordling here (or Kuruon if hes up). 
<br />
8. Run into the Northeast hall now and pull the discordling that passes in front of Ghio's spawn point. 
<br />
9. This is the tricky one and how I pull it is to use my mezz song (the 67 version works here) but by this time the respawn is due within 1-2 mins, sometimes less so hurry. In this area youll see 3 mobs, 2 to the side of a platform (which are not lullable) and 1 on the platform (which is also not lullable). Use boastful Bellow or use Requim of time/dispel to pull 1 of the mobs to the side and you will get that mob + Ghio or his PH. Run down the hall and mezz the mob that is not Ghio or his PH right were the hall opens into the open area. Turn mezz off pull Ghio/PH to your group and Fade just before the tank gets arrgo and the last mob will not add. Instead it will go back to its spawn point. If you mezz gets resisted just bring it with you.
<br />
10. Run directly west from your camp and face south till you see a wandering mob. When it is NOT moving pull it to your group. If you pull it while its moving east Odi or her PH will add. 
<br />
11. Once the wanderer is dead go down the south hall and pull Odi. 
<br />
12. By now the 1st mob has respawned so rinse and repeat. 
<br />

<br />
If your confused get a map from mapfiend.com and it should help clear stuff up. If you have questions please feel free to ask and Ill try to answer them.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
